/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151183980702b0f9380c194c4f76bff4dbbc3562","tid":2402841,"uid":141833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776a6421ebcd61b60c1a30b0ab70fef185619831","tid":2402841,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"不嬲用口吮"},{"pid":"99831dfd128cdb780d987158291bdbec65fe7425","tid":2402841,"uid":42588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"睇咗咇尿女醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60239416c8924ef1756a3c298cee25b67369172","tid":2402841,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"條女咁一舊水feel"},{"pid":"7058f094ca817d305a629244caae34ae1ccb7cc3","tid":2402841,"uid":292585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c814e5e26cedb2a213b41403c89568d6ed2bf4e","tid":2402841,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T20:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_K7vDVl5sq1k/SvLAncyf6RI/AAAAAAAAF3w/4AByxt95tvs/s400/bobo_next1026_006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F_K7vDVl5sq1k%2FSvLAncyf6RI%2FAAAAAAAAF3w%2F4AByxt95tvs%2Fs400%2Fbobo_next1026_006.jpg&h=39f729f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"一舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}